00:40:01,766 --> 00:40:03,800
<i>Te peguei!</i>

536
00:40:12,566 --> 00:40:16,166
<i>Nossa! Vamos brincar mais.</i>

537
00:40:17,166 --> 00:40:19,966
<i>Brincar?</i>

538
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:23,633
<i>Sim. Vamos brincar
</i>

