588
00:44:45,594 --> 00:44:47,761
Marquei a fronteira ao norte.

589
00:44:47,761 --> 00:44:49,761
Verá quando partir.

590
00:44:51,761 --> 00:44:53,394
Que diabos quer dizer com isso?

591
00:44:54,427 --> 00:44:56,261
Verá quando partir.

592
00:44:56,894 --> 00:44:57,927
Vá.

593
00:44:58,427 --> 00:44:59,994
Suas amigas o esperam

594
00:44:59,994 --> 00:45:01,261
