Quero ficar sozinha.

628
00:49:28,659 --> 00:49:29,726
Siddiq!

629
00:49:37,926 --> 00:49:39,259
O que houve?

630
00:49:41,692 --> 00:49:46,092
Eu... Eu...

631
00:50:55,826 --> 00:50:58,226
Nabila, olá. Viu Frankie?

632
00:51:10,592 --> 00:51:11,892
